Connection
# Note: Use WebSocket client to connect to this endpoint
# ws://localhost:8386/v1/ws?user_id=user123

### Broadcast Message to All Users
POST http://localhost:8386/v1/ws/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello everyone!",
  "sender": "admin"
}

### Send Message to Specific User
POST http://localhost:8386/v1/ws/send/user123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello user123!",
  "sender": "admin",
  "type": "notification"
}

### Get Online Users
GET http://localhost:8386/v1/ws/online